A political group, Advocates for Bola Ahmed Tinubu 2023 Agenda (A4BAT), has declared support for Tinubu’s 2023 presidential bid. The body, in a statement by the National Chairman, Okoye Tochukwu, said it was determined to support Tinubu’s ambition to the best of its ability.   Body to restore schools’ glory     House of Reps Aspirant seeks unity in Osun APC      Lagos trains officers to aid competence   The statement reads: “There may be no better time than now for us to declare our support and loyalty to back the dreams and aspirations of our principal, Asiwaju Tinubu, in his quest for the 2023 presidential slot. “We are the Advocates for Bola Ahmed Tinubu (A4BAT 2023 Agenda) in Nigeria and beyond. We are a formidable group of professionals, technocrats and trained socio-political experts with proven records from all walks of life. “We are out to support the ambition of our principal, Asiwaju Tinubu, to the best of our ability.”